WEBVTT

00:39.820 --> 00:41.280
This wine was just warmed.

00:41.790 --> 00:43.320
Have a cup to warm yourself.

00:49.110 --> 00:51.310
Water chestnut and lily bulb pastries.

00:55.320 --> 00:57.030
With the Yan Army
stationed outside the pass

00:57.030 --> 00:58.830
and the people gripped by panic,

00:59.240 --> 01:01.900
it's rare to find shops
still open on the street.

01:02.340 --> 01:04.800
Lin Mu went out specially
to buy these today.

01:05.430 --> 01:06.760
These bulb pastries...

01:07.560 --> 01:08.280
Yan Xun

01:09.430 --> 01:10.890
used to love them the most.

01:13.510 --> 01:15.039
But that was a long time ago.

01:17.230 --> 01:20.789
During those years when Yan Xun and I
were in the Yingge Courtyard,

01:20.789 --> 01:22.250
we lived in fear every day.

01:22.830 --> 01:25.340
We didn't dare eat any food
that was sent to us.

01:25.340 --> 01:27.420
Only after catching live mice
to test for poison

01:27.420 --> 01:28.950
would we dare eat anything.

01:30.070 --> 01:31.070
During that time,

01:31.700 --> 01:33.250
not a single meal we had

01:33.430 --> 01:34.680
was fresh.

01:35.160 --> 01:37.470
In the height of summer,

01:38.150 --> 01:40.479
the food we ate was already spoiled.

01:41.000 --> 01:41.950
Only Chun'er

01:42.570 --> 01:43.970
still cared about Yan Xun

01:44.910 --> 01:47.640
and would sometimes send over
some good food.

01:49.710 --> 01:50.560
Once,

01:52.120 --> 01:55.220
Yan Xun ate the water chestnut
and lily bulb pastries she had sent

01:55.220 --> 01:56.220
and was poisoned.

01:56.509 --> 01:57.509
I was terrified,

01:58.430 --> 01:59.680
afraid he would die.

02:00.710 --> 02:02.440
I went through so much trouble—

02:02.920 --> 02:03.850
begging for help

02:04.350 --> 02:05.560
and searching for medicine—

02:05.560 --> 02:07.950
before I managed to pull him back
from the brink of death.

02:07.950 --> 02:09.610
To this day, I still don't know

02:10.000 --> 02:11.930
who poisoned Chun'er's pastries.

02:12.520 --> 02:15.050
Chun'er herself
probably never knew either.

02:15.750 --> 02:16.710
After that,

02:17.590 --> 02:19.800
she still kept sending the pastries.

02:20.310 --> 02:22.430
Every time, Yan Xun would pretend
nothing had happened

02:22.430 --> 02:23.760
and devour the pastries

02:23.840 --> 02:25.710
right in front of her.

02:26.680 --> 02:27.840
Only I knew

02:28.680 --> 02:30.630
that the water chestnut
and lily bulb pastries

02:30.630 --> 02:32.030
had long become the thing

02:32.590 --> 02:34.050
he hated most in the world.

02:42.280 --> 02:43.190
From now on,

02:44.310 --> 02:46.240
I won't let Lin Mu buy them anymore.

02:47.150 --> 02:48.000
Zhuge Yue,

02:49.680 --> 02:51.010
you and I are different.

02:51.270 --> 02:53.360
I grew up as a slave in Qingshan Manor.

02:55.240 --> 02:57.750
I don't even know my parents' names.

02:58.560 --> 02:59.310
But you—

03:00.290 --> 03:03.080
you're the noble young master
of the illustrious Zhuge family

03:03.080 --> 03:04.810
and the heir to Qingshan Manor.

03:05.200 --> 03:07.400
There has always been a gulf between us.

03:08.630 --> 03:09.310
Xing,

03:10.560 --> 03:12.490
what exactly are you trying to say?

03:14.200 --> 03:16.060
You don't need to stay here at all.

03:16.310 --> 03:18.110
You should go back to Great Yong,

03:18.120 --> 03:19.250
to the Zhuge family.

03:19.560 --> 03:20.470
Tell them

03:21.430 --> 03:22.829
that you're still alive.

03:25.840 --> 03:27.240
So you're saying all this

03:28.590 --> 03:29.870
just to make me leave?

03:30.400 --> 03:32.000
You shouldn't be doing this—

03:32.079 --> 03:33.740
holding out here alongside me

03:33.840 --> 03:35.590
without even a proper identity.

03:35.590 --> 03:36.430
This isn't the life you should be living.

03:36.430 --> 03:37.290
What about you?

03:40.210 --> 03:43.160
Walk out and surrender to Yan Xun?

03:44.000 --> 03:46.060
You know full well that is his scheme.

03:56.840 --> 03:59.370
The sun and moon cannot shine
at the same time.

03:59.470 --> 04:00.560
The sun and the moon

04:01.360 --> 04:02.310
can never share the same sky

04:02.310 --> 04:03.870
at the same time.

04:16.230 --> 04:18.160
The sun and moon shining together—

04:18.560 --> 04:19.820
I'll take you to see it.

05:52.390 --> 05:57.700
[REBIRTH]

05:58.150 --> 06:00.700
[Episode 21]

06:23.270 --> 06:24.080
Zhuge Yue...

06:25.900 --> 06:26.670
I'm leaving.

06:28.240 --> 06:31.040
You've guarded the pass alongside me
for so many days.

06:31.040 --> 06:33.770
I don't want you to
sacrifice any more for my sake.

06:35.000 --> 06:36.070
When you wake up,

06:37.070 --> 06:38.190
forget about me.

06:40.430 --> 06:43.630
Go back to being the Young Master Zhuge
of Qingshan Manor.

06:49.070 --> 06:51.690
[Urgent military situation. I'm heading
to Great Yong to secure supplies.]

06:51.690 --> 06:54.310
[General Chu is in danger. I'll handle
the provisions. Do not worry. —Zhuge Yue]

06:55.040 --> 06:57.500
The guard
who has been following General Chu

06:57.600 --> 06:59.120
is General Zhuge of Great Yong?

06:59.120 --> 06:59.720
Yes.

07:00.630 --> 07:02.040
So please don't worry, General Li.

07:02.040 --> 07:04.150
Since General Zhuge said he would
borrow provisions from Great Yong,

07:04.150 --> 07:06.610
he will certainly not return empty-handed.

07:17.440 --> 07:18.980
Stop! Stop!

07:38.409 --> 07:39.810
His Majesty has arrived!

07:52.159 --> 07:52.870
Chu,

07:54.120 --> 07:55.000
I knew

07:56.070 --> 07:57.470
you would come back to me.

07:57.800 --> 07:58.390
Come on.

07:58.950 --> 08:00.040
Let me show you the gifts

08:00.040 --> 08:01.360
I've prepared for you.

08:02.680 --> 08:04.340
I've been waiting for this day

08:05.480 --> 08:06.480
for a long time.

08:19.830 --> 08:20.560
Chu,

08:22.040 --> 08:24.040
I prepared this especially for you.

08:24.680 --> 08:26.140
It's your favorite style.

08:26.630 --> 08:27.430
Do you like it?

08:31.830 --> 08:33.510
To make it easier for you
to ride and shoot,

08:33.510 --> 08:35.000
I had it specially altered.

08:35.000 --> 08:35.799
There's more.

08:36.480 --> 08:38.140
These pieces of jewelry here.

08:38.510 --> 08:39.870
According to your preferences,

08:39.870 --> 08:42.840
I had them custom-made to
the standard of the Queen of Great Yan.

08:42.840 --> 08:44.100
If you don't like them,

08:44.670 --> 08:46.120
I'll have them changed immediately

08:46.120 --> 08:48.050
until you find something you like.

08:54.790 --> 08:55.480
Chu,

08:56.680 --> 08:57.560
don't do this.

09:07.200 --> 09:08.860
Degrading yourself like this

09:08.870 --> 09:10.080
won't provoke me.

09:20.150 --> 09:21.550
If you're satisfied now,

09:22.200 --> 09:23.660
please honor your promise

09:23.790 --> 09:25.590
and order your army to withdraw.

09:26.480 --> 09:28.000
The weather is turning cold.

09:28.000 --> 09:29.660
If this stalemate continues,

09:30.070 --> 09:32.510
not only will the Biantang soldiers
not be able to hold on,

09:32.510 --> 09:35.600
but your soldiers may also not endure.

09:36.240 --> 09:36.930
Chu,

09:37.670 --> 09:39.670
I'll keep my promise to you.

09:40.150 --> 09:41.120
Do you remember?

09:42.000 --> 09:42.960
I once told you

09:43.380 --> 09:45.440
that I'd prove to you that I was right.

09:46.320 --> 09:49.200
I'll conquer the world
and lay it at your feet.

09:49.480 --> 09:50.880
I'll withdraw my troops.

09:51.080 --> 09:51.630
Just

09:52.390 --> 09:53.360
not now.

09:58.750 --> 09:59.480
Chu,

10:00.960 --> 10:02.000
just stay here

10:02.600 --> 10:03.800
and wait for me.

10:08.240 --> 10:09.360
Protect the Queen.

10:09.630 --> 10:11.200
If anything happens to her,

10:11.740 --> 10:14.270
neither of you
will return to Great Yan alive.

10:21.840 --> 10:22.700
Your Highness.

10:43.670 --> 10:45.630
Your Majesty is dressed so plainly,

10:45.630 --> 10:48.080
without any jewelry

10:48.840 --> 10:49.750
except for

10:49.750 --> 10:51.610
the hairpin His Majesty gave you.

10:53.880 --> 10:55.610
Your devotion to His Majesty

10:55.910 --> 10:57.550
runs truly deep.

11:10.750 --> 11:12.150
May I remind Your Majesty

11:12.630 --> 11:15.990
that His Majesty had the double cross lock
made especially for you.

11:15.990 --> 11:17.870
Rather than exhausting yourself
trying to unlock it,

11:17.870 --> 11:19.670
you might as well eat something.

11:20.000 --> 11:22.030
The roasted mutton and hawthorn cake

11:22.030 --> 11:24.300
were specially prepared for you
by the camp cooks

11:24.300 --> 11:25.760
at His Majesty's request.

11:25.960 --> 11:27.560
They are all your favorites.

11:28.420 --> 11:30.680
Consort Helian, you're so considerate.

11:36.200 --> 11:37.840
And Your Majesty is a clever woman, too.

11:37.840 --> 11:39.900
You should know that no one could ever

11:40.390 --> 11:42.390
replace you in His Majesty's heart.

11:42.480 --> 11:44.080
Given His Majesty's temperament,

11:44.080 --> 11:45.390
if you refuse to yield,

11:45.790 --> 11:47.520
he will never back down either.

11:48.960 --> 11:50.600
Rather than both of you suffering,

11:50.600 --> 11:52.840
it would be better to accept his feelings.

11:52.840 --> 11:53.900
Come to think of it,

11:55.480 --> 11:56.780
I never had the chance

11:57.670 --> 11:59.600
to thank you for helping me before.

12:00.720 --> 12:02.550
I don't know what you're talking about.

12:02.550 --> 12:04.610
On the way back to Great Yan last time,

12:05.080 --> 12:07.030
if you hadn't pretended to lose your way

12:07.030 --> 12:09.270
and helped General Cheng
draw Yan Xun away,

12:09.270 --> 12:11.120
how could General Cheng have
had the chance to let me go?

12:11.120 --> 12:12.840
I'm only a minor consort.

12:13.080 --> 12:15.140
All I can do is serve His Majesty well.

12:15.390 --> 12:17.550
As for helping General Cheng
draw him away,

12:17.550 --> 12:20.240
I have neither the ability
nor the courage.

12:20.390 --> 12:23.520
Since you were willing to
cooperate with General Cheng,

12:24.030 --> 12:26.750
you surely don't want to see me
remain at Yan Xun's side.

12:26.750 --> 12:28.080
You should be very clear

12:28.120 --> 12:30.630
that Yan Xun's marriage alliance
with your Helian Tribe

12:30.630 --> 12:31.960
was what temporarily stabilized

12:31.960 --> 12:34.390
those fierce and predatory tribes
of Great Yan.

12:34.390 --> 12:36.200
If he takes me back now,

12:36.750 --> 12:38.480
it will certainly cause
a tremendous uproar

12:38.480 --> 12:40.600
among the various tribes of Great Yan

12:41.000 --> 12:42.480
and plunge the state into turmoil.

12:42.480 --> 12:44.140
And when that turmoil begins,

12:44.710 --> 12:46.160
I would wager your tribe

12:46.510 --> 12:48.150
will be the first to suffer.

12:48.150 --> 12:49.120
Enough!

12:49.630 --> 12:51.000
I'm not you,

12:52.200 --> 12:53.750
nor do I command an army.

12:55.550 --> 12:57.680
What happens in Great Yan in the future

12:58.440 --> 13:00.300
is not something I can influence.

13:05.050 --> 13:05.560
[Biantang and Great Yan have been at a standoff
for months. The situation is dire.]

13:05.560 --> 13:05.820
[If Longyin Pass falls, the enemy
will push south. Tangjing will fall,]

13:05.820 --> 13:06.080
[and Great Yong will follow.
This is a case of shared fate.]

13:06.100 --> 13:06.610
[Biantang is prosperous, but we're unprepared
for war and short on supplies.]

13:06.610 --> 13:06.870
[We earnestly request Great Yong's military aid
and a temporary loan of provisions.]

13:06.870 --> 13:07.130
[With your aid, our combined forces
will surely repel Great Yan.]

13:07.150 --> 13:07.620
[After the war, Biantang will repay this kindness
and forge a lasting friendship with Great Yong.]

13:07.620 --> 13:08.100
[For the sake of both nations' people,
please do not refuse.]

13:10.400 --> 13:14.640
The new Emperor of Biantang wants to
borrow troops and provisions from us?

13:14.960 --> 13:17.760
Biantang and Great Yan have been
at war for months.

13:18.080 --> 13:20.540
If you're willing to
lend a helping hand now,

13:20.870 --> 13:23.790
we can surely defeat the Black Eagle Army
of Great Yan in one fell swoop.

13:23.790 --> 13:24.910
Biantang has

13:25.270 --> 13:26.600
always been far more prosperous than us—

13:26.600 --> 13:28.080
and even more so than Great Yan.

13:28.080 --> 13:30.270
Though you were caught off guard
this time,

13:30.270 --> 13:32.670
with some adjustment,
you might still win.

13:33.150 --> 13:34.320
The battle at Meilin Pass

13:34.320 --> 13:35.750
cost us dearly.

13:36.200 --> 13:38.670
Our entire army
has been recuperating ever since.

13:38.670 --> 13:40.910
If I rashly send troops to assist now,

13:41.670 --> 13:43.120
I fear it would only backfire.

13:43.120 --> 13:46.600
Our two states are like lips and teeth—
neither can survive without the other.

13:46.600 --> 13:48.840
If the Black Eagle Army
breaks through Longyin Pass

13:48.840 --> 13:50.900
and sweeps south along the Red River,

13:50.960 --> 13:53.560
Tangjing will be lost,
and Biantang will fall.

13:54.030 --> 13:56.510
When the Black Eagle Army reaches
Zhenhuangcheng,

13:56.510 --> 13:57.750
what you will lose...

13:59.120 --> 14:01.050
will be the lifeline of the empire.

14:05.480 --> 14:06.390
Who are you?

14:07.270 --> 14:10.800
How do you know our country's terrain
like the back of your hand?

14:15.960 --> 14:18.200
I'm an envoy of Biantang.

14:18.910 --> 14:19.950
An envoy?

14:37.620 --> 14:40.070
You remind me of a friend.

14:40.940 --> 14:43.390
I once fought alongside him
on the battlefield.

14:43.390 --> 14:45.120
But he was gone before I was.

14:45.480 --> 14:46.670
I never believed

14:47.670 --> 14:50.070
he was the kind of person
others said he was.

15:05.000 --> 15:07.000
Since he chose to go first,

15:07.910 --> 15:10.570
it must mean
he found something more important.

15:11.480 --> 15:12.440
Your Highness

15:13.360 --> 15:14.590
may as well let him go.

15:21.510 --> 15:23.320
I have 50,000 dans of surplus grain

15:23.320 --> 15:25.250
to tide you over in this emergency.

15:25.360 --> 15:26.620
As for sending troops,

15:26.720 --> 15:29.050
I must first seek His Majesty's approval.

15:29.070 --> 15:30.800
I cannot give you an answer yet.

15:33.150 --> 15:34.610
Thank you, Your Highness.

15:52.630 --> 15:54.360
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

16:09.080 --> 16:09.840
Chu,

16:11.720 --> 16:12.920
you're so beautiful.

16:18.900 --> 16:19.570
Am I?

16:26.960 --> 16:27.630
Yes.

16:29.240 --> 16:32.240
I've imagined you like this for so long.

16:32.840 --> 16:33.510
Chu,

16:33.810 --> 16:35.240
when we return to Great Yan,

16:35.240 --> 16:36.900
I'll rouge your lips every day

16:37.030 --> 16:38.530
and take you to watch
the four seasons change on the grassland,

16:38.530 --> 16:39.290
okay?

16:42.710 --> 16:44.770
Why wait until we return to Great Yan?

16:45.000 --> 16:47.530
Why not take me outside
for some fresh air now?

17:00.150 --> 17:02.280
You should feel reassured now, right?

17:13.510 --> 17:14.310
Chu,

17:15.400 --> 17:16.839
no matter where you run,

17:19.480 --> 17:20.920
I will find you.

17:53.880 --> 17:54.510
Chu,

17:55.220 --> 17:57.220
every soldier in my Black Eagle Army

17:57.340 --> 17:59.270
is the best of the best.

17:59.640 --> 18:01.600
Dealing with a handful of
feeble Biantang soldiers at once

18:01.600 --> 18:02.530
is nothing to us.

18:43.850 --> 18:44.520
Chu,

18:45.480 --> 18:46.940
we have ample grain stores

18:47.200 --> 18:49.260
with continuous supplies coming in.

18:49.960 --> 18:52.830
Even if we have to fight through
an entire winter against Biantang,

18:52.830 --> 18:54.030
it won't be a problem.

19:09.590 --> 19:10.400
Chu.

19:12.510 --> 19:14.110
I'm so happy today.

19:15.350 --> 19:17.270
If things could always be

19:17.480 --> 19:19.350
like this between us—

19:20.530 --> 19:22.460
no longer at each other's throats—

19:23.340 --> 19:25.210
I wouldn't need this cage

19:25.510 --> 19:26.590
to keep you here.

19:27.640 --> 19:28.510
Really?

19:28.960 --> 19:32.160
My promise to you has never changed.

19:44.310 --> 19:46.310
You want to take me back to Great Yan.

19:46.350 --> 19:48.010
Then what about your consort?

19:52.070 --> 19:52.830
Chu,

19:53.790 --> 19:54.790
in my heart,

19:56.220 --> 19:58.630
there has only ever been you.

19:59.310 --> 20:00.550
If you don't like her,

20:00.830 --> 20:02.310
when we return to Great Yan,

20:02.310 --> 20:03.970
I'll let her leave the palace.

20:04.160 --> 20:06.310
Helian Ling isn't just a consort now.

20:06.830 --> 20:07.830
Behind her

20:08.000 --> 20:10.270
stands the support of the elders
of the various tribes in Great Yan.

20:10.270 --> 20:12.160
If you let her go now,

20:14.280 --> 20:17.280
how do you plan to face those elders?

20:17.350 --> 20:18.830
The Helian Tribe is weak,

20:19.220 --> 20:20.820
and Helian Chuan is useless.

20:21.260 --> 20:23.550
If I hadn't made Helian Ling my consort,

20:23.880 --> 20:25.240
their tribe's pastures

20:26.480 --> 20:29.210
would've been carved up
by other tribes long ago.

20:53.510 --> 20:54.030
Speak.

20:54.930 --> 20:56.260
What do you want me to do?

20:57.260 --> 20:59.120
What do you mean, Consort Helian?

20:59.680 --> 21:02.080
Yesterday, you knew
I was outside the tent,

21:02.320 --> 21:05.000
yet you deliberately tried to
sow discord between His Majesty and me.

21:05.000 --> 21:06.930
Didn't you just want me to help you?

21:07.900 --> 21:08.510
Go ahead.

23:23.200 --> 23:24.860
Go notify Lin Mu and the others

23:24.960 --> 23:26.960
to assemble 50 of the most elite soldiers
from the Xiuli Army

23:26.960 --> 23:27.750
into a squad

23:28.200 --> 23:30.380
and set out with me
at first light tomorrow.

23:30.380 --> 23:30.940
Yes, sir.

23:35.000 --> 23:36.880
[Great Yan's grain convoy will pass through
the forest outside Longyin Pass tomorrow.]

23:36.880 --> 23:38.760
[This is an opportunity.
Bring men and seize the grain immediately.]

24:05.290 --> 24:07.300
Take both the men and the grain!

24:07.400 --> 24:07.790
Yes, sir.

24:07.790 --> 24:08.300
Yes, sir.

24:08.300 --> 24:09.100
-Move.
-Move.

24:13.960 --> 24:14.440
Young Master,

24:14.440 --> 24:15.510
there's something wrong with the grain.

24:15.510 --> 24:16.310
It's all sand!

24:22.120 --> 24:24.350
When I brought food to Her Majesty today,

24:24.350 --> 24:27.000
I unexpectedly caught her
trying to use this hairpin

24:27.000 --> 24:28.800
to pick the lock on the iron cage.

24:29.720 --> 24:32.660
Not only did she disregard
Your Majesty's affection for her,

24:32.660 --> 24:34.590
but she even tried to manipulate me

24:34.600 --> 24:36.630
into helping her escape.

24:37.220 --> 24:38.950
Since she wants you to help her,

24:39.990 --> 24:40.920
why don't you...

24:43.310 --> 24:44.630
help her then?

24:49.550 --> 24:51.270
Oh no, it's a trap!

25:01.330 --> 25:01.890
Retreat!

25:04.160 --> 25:04.720
Retreat!

25:09.360 --> 25:10.160
Young Master,

25:10.290 --> 25:11.280
I'll lead some men to distract them.

25:11.280 --> 25:12.080
Alright, go.

25:16.400 --> 25:16.960
Stop!

25:18.110 --> 25:18.670
This way!

25:21.810 --> 25:22.470
After them!

25:23.130 --> 25:23.650
Hurry!

25:28.730 --> 25:29.830
It's a cliff down here.

25:29.830 --> 25:31.460
Fall off that,
and you're dead or crippled.

25:31.460 --> 25:32.220
Let's go!

25:32.700 --> 25:33.500
Go!

25:43.790 --> 25:46.070
We've been at a stalemate
with the Biantang army for days,

25:46.070 --> 25:48.160
and they have been behind their walls.

25:48.160 --> 25:48.750
Now,

25:49.270 --> 25:51.400
General Chu Qiao of Biantang's Xiuli Army

25:51.400 --> 25:52.800
is in my camp in Great Yan,

25:52.920 --> 25:55.980
and the main force of the Xiuli Army
was ambushed today.

25:57.030 --> 25:58.830
Longyin Pass is now leaderless.

25:59.310 --> 26:00.640
We will depart tonight,

26:01.160 --> 26:02.360
press our advantage,

26:02.680 --> 26:04.130
and take Longyin Pass in one fell swoop!

26:04.130 --> 26:05.760
Yes, Your Majesty!

26:33.270 --> 26:33.920
Stop!

26:36.960 --> 26:37.760
Your Majesty,

26:37.960 --> 26:38.790
it's already broad daylight.

26:38.790 --> 26:39.630
The scouts report

26:39.630 --> 26:41.270
that the gates of Longyin Pass
are still tightly shut

26:41.270 --> 26:42.600
with no signs of activity.

26:42.600 --> 26:44.190
Logically, Biantang's sentries

26:44.190 --> 26:46.110
should've already learned
that we've mobilized.

26:46.110 --> 26:46.790
I'm just worried...

26:46.790 --> 26:47.480
Pass on my orders—

26:47.480 --> 26:49.480
full army advances swiftly
through the valley

26:49.480 --> 26:50.550
and strikes the pass directly!

26:50.550 --> 26:51.350
Your Majesty.

26:53.000 --> 26:53.480
March!

26:53.480 --> 26:54.030
Hurry!

27:06.140 --> 27:06.940
Your Majesty,

27:07.000 --> 27:08.250
the terrain ahead is treacherous.

27:08.250 --> 27:09.510
Why don't I go first...

27:12.310 --> 27:13.070
Ambush!

27:17.940 --> 27:18.440
Fire!

28:08.540 --> 28:09.980
Zhuge Yue.

28:10.760 --> 28:12.020
This letter is forged.

28:12.790 --> 28:15.330
It doesn't have the secret code
of Qingshan Manor on it.

28:15.330 --> 28:18.000
This lantern came from the direction
of the Great Yan military camp.

28:18.000 --> 28:18.880
Only General Chu

28:18.880 --> 28:20.590
knows our method of messaging
at Qingshan Manor.

28:20.590 --> 28:21.240
Then why would she

28:21.240 --> 28:22.790
send us a false message?

28:23.030 --> 28:23.830
Notify Lin Mu

28:24.080 --> 28:25.680
to assemble the elites of the Xiuli Army

28:25.680 --> 28:27.160
and set out immediately tonight.

28:27.160 --> 28:27.720
Yes, sir.

28:28.360 --> 28:28.950
Wait.

28:29.830 --> 28:30.780
And tell He Xiao

28:30.830 --> 28:32.090
to set out immediately

28:32.240 --> 28:33.640
to 50 li outside Longyin Pass

28:33.640 --> 28:35.640
to meet Zhao Che's reinforcements.

29:42.440 --> 29:43.170
General Chu?

29:47.750 --> 29:48.480
General Chu?

29:54.510 --> 29:55.240
General Chu?

29:55.750 --> 29:56.610
Someone, come!

29:58.540 --> 30:00.240
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness!

30:00.240 --> 30:01.240
Open the door.

30:03.440 --> 30:04.240
Open the door!

30:14.830 --> 30:15.880
Be careful.

30:22.160 --> 30:23.960
Catch her! Don't let her escape!

30:28.330 --> 30:29.200
Catch her!

30:34.570 --> 30:35.770
Don't let her escape!

30:52.240 --> 30:52.960
Stop!

31:12.640 --> 31:14.310
Help! Fire!

31:24.510 --> 31:25.710
Hurry! Keep chasing!

31:26.270 --> 31:27.760
Go back and put out the fire!

31:27.760 --> 31:29.020
The granary is on fire!

31:29.160 --> 31:30.070
Get water!

31:30.470 --> 31:30.990
Quick!

32:20.320 --> 32:21.120
Your Majesty.

33:02.790 --> 33:05.000
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

33:05.110 --> 33:07.660
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

33:08.090 --> 33:09.390
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

33:09.420 --> 33:10.880
♪ My longing surges ♪

33:10.900 --> 33:13.410
♪ I become haggard ♪

33:14.020 --> 33:16.460
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

33:16.510 --> 33:19.330
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

33:19.350 --> 33:21.050
♪ My love remains ♪

33:21.360 --> 33:24.730
♪ But you're already gone ♪

33:24.760 --> 33:27.030
♪ What I seek in life ♪

33:27.050 --> 33:28.640
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

33:28.660 --> 33:31.250
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

33:31.270 --> 33:32.860
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

33:32.880 --> 33:36.070
♪ My longing still rests ♪

33:36.090 --> 33:38.450
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

33:38.030 --> 33:38.750
Zhuge Yue,

33:38.480 --> 33:39.990
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

33:39.590 --> 33:40.400
you've beaten me again.

33:40.010 --> 33:42.650
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

33:42.690 --> 33:47.550
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

33:43.310 --> 33:44.510
I beat you every time.

33:45.230 --> 33:46.830
Why do you never get mad at me?

33:47.580 --> 33:48.970
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

33:49.000 --> 33:51.250
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

33:51.270 --> 33:53.720
♪ How do we start over? ♪

33:52.720 --> 33:54.240
Keep your hands to yourself.

33:53.740 --> 33:57.050
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

33:57.080 --> 33:59.330
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

33:59.360 --> 34:02.770
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

34:02.110 --> 34:02.960
Because...

34:02.790 --> 34:05.110
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

34:04.790 --> 34:06.160
you're my only friend.

34:05.130 --> 34:08.010
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

34:06.720 --> 34:08.480
We will never truly
stand on opposing sides.

34:08.040 --> 34:11.300
♪ In the end ♪

34:41.250 --> 34:42.050
Your Majesty,

34:42.320 --> 34:43.179
let's retreat.

34:43.590 --> 34:45.190
It'll be too late if we don't!

34:46.880 --> 34:47.810
Pass on my order:

34:48.440 --> 34:50.100
full army withdraws by the same route!

34:50.100 --> 34:51.159
His Majesty orders

34:51.230 --> 34:53.030
a full retreat by the same route!

35:01.230 --> 35:02.030
Your Majesty!

35:02.530 --> 35:03.250
Your Majesty,

35:03.250 --> 35:05.480
Li Qi has led the Biantang Army
to block our retreat from behind.

35:05.480 --> 35:06.850
Our main camp has also been set on fire!

35:06.850 --> 35:07.780
We can't go back!

35:08.110 --> 35:08.910
Your Majesty,

35:09.150 --> 35:11.000
let the remaining Black Eagle Army
hold off Zhuge Yue

35:11.000 --> 35:12.800
while you immediately retreat
through Rongguan Path

35:12.800 --> 35:13.320
and return to Great Yan!

35:13.320 --> 35:13.880
No!

35:15.270 --> 35:16.950
I can't leave the Black Eagle Army behind.

35:16.950 --> 35:18.550
I brought them here.

35:18.630 --> 35:19.480
As long as we live,

35:19.480 --> 35:20.590
we can fight another day!

35:20.590 --> 35:21.880
If anything happens to Your Majesty,

35:21.880 --> 35:24.280
Great Yan will have no chance
to rise again!

35:25.670 --> 35:28.550
Please return to Great Yan at once,
Your Majesty!

35:31.060 --> 35:33.190
Let's retreat through Rongguan Path.

35:33.240 --> 35:33.990
Guys,

35:34.190 --> 35:35.720
follow me to cover the rear!

35:38.830 --> 35:39.390
Go!

35:49.660 --> 35:50.460
Young Master,

35:50.670 --> 35:51.930
Yan Xun didn't return.

35:52.190 --> 35:54.880
He led a small group of men
and ran toward the valley.

35:54.880 --> 35:56.880
Li Qi's troops have cut off his rear.

35:57.240 --> 35:58.840
He won't walk into that trap.

35:58.880 --> 36:00.550
His only option is to stake everything

36:00.550 --> 36:01.960
and take Rongguan Path instead.

36:01.960 --> 36:02.820
Rongguan Path?

36:03.410 --> 36:04.820
Isn't that an abandoned route?

36:04.820 --> 36:05.840
It's full of swamps and lakes.

36:05.840 --> 36:07.570
One wrong step and you're dead.

36:07.710 --> 36:09.460
The terrain of Rongguan Path
is treacherous.

36:09.460 --> 36:11.070
Not only is fleeing through it dangerous,

36:11.070 --> 36:14.000
but pursuing them
will also be extremely difficult.

36:14.030 --> 36:15.360
Given Yan Xun's nature,

36:16.280 --> 36:18.050
he will certainly
take this desperate gamble.

36:18.050 --> 36:18.850
Young Master,

36:18.880 --> 36:20.150
we can't let them escape.

36:20.150 --> 36:21.750
Let's pursue them right now.

36:56.080 --> 36:57.610
Your Majesty, you go first.

36:57.710 --> 36:58.840
I'll cover the rear.

37:03.590 --> 37:04.800
I'll go intercept Yan Xun.

37:04.800 --> 37:05.880
You guys split up!

37:17.800 --> 37:18.400
Kill them!

37:47.800 --> 37:48.470
Chu,

37:48.960 --> 37:50.370
now that things have come to this,

37:50.370 --> 37:53.440
dying at your hands
would be no great regret.

37:53.920 --> 37:55.230
If you want to kill me,

37:56.230 --> 37:57.400
then come and do it.

38:25.370 --> 38:27.540
[Yan Shicheng]

38:38.880 --> 38:39.610
How do you...

38:41.440 --> 38:42.640
How do you have these?

38:42.790 --> 38:44.240
After what happened at Jiuyou Platform,

38:44.240 --> 38:48.220
♪ The sky is so vast ♪

38:45.280 --> 38:46.400
I asked Zhao Song

38:47.840 --> 38:50.190
to help me collect them
from their bodies, one by one.

38:48.240 --> 38:50.730
♪ The dark clouds are gray ♪

38:50.840 --> 38:52.100
Originally, I thought

38:52.550 --> 38:53.800
that one day

38:53.120 --> 38:56.880
♪ The rain is falling ♪

38:54.190 --> 38:56.440
you and I would avenge them together.

38:56.900 --> 39:00.260
♪ The eagle is flying ♪

38:58.690 --> 39:01.880
Once you had made peace with
what happened at Jiuyou Platform,

39:01.880 --> 39:03.710
I would give them to you properly.

39:02.310 --> 39:06.100
♪ In the vast wilderness ♪

39:04.840 --> 39:05.840
But now,

39:06.120 --> 39:09.590
♪ The wind blows ♪

39:07.520 --> 39:09.920
maybe there'll never be that chance again.

39:11.020 --> 39:11.750
Yan Xun,

39:11.620 --> 39:14.690
♪ I'm fearless of death ♪

39:12.980 --> 39:14.270
think of your family.

39:14.920 --> 39:18.440
♪ And I'll never have regrets ♪

39:15.020 --> 39:16.510
Think about your father.

39:17.670 --> 39:20.820
He was loyal and devoted to his people
and his country all his life.

39:20.770 --> 39:28.290
♪ The lonely black eagle ♪

39:21.670 --> 39:24.470
Now, the people of Great Yan
are living in misery.

39:25.040 --> 39:26.570
Is this the Great Yan

39:26.970 --> 39:28.460
you want him to see?

39:29.070 --> 39:30.780
Do you want to live in hatred forever?

39:29.540 --> 39:32.910
♪ Is flying against the light ♪

39:32.480 --> 39:33.920
I'll give you two choices.

39:33.720 --> 39:36.920
♪ Where is my hometown? ♪

39:35.790 --> 39:36.400
Either

39:37.440 --> 39:39.520
we fight to the death here today—

39:37.460 --> 39:46.420
♪ In the vast world ♪

39:39.920 --> 39:40.880
only one of us

39:40.880 --> 39:42.480
walks out alive—

39:44.670 --> 39:45.610
or...

39:46.440 --> 39:49.850
♪ I have no origin ♪

39:48.000 --> 39:49.200
for the next 10 years,

39:49.480 --> 39:51.920
you are not to set foot in Biantang again!

39:50.500 --> 39:54.100
♪ And no destination ♪

39:54.670 --> 40:02.720
♪ A pair of stubborn wings ♪

40:02.840 --> 40:11.120
♪ Is born to fly ♪

40:13.020 --> 40:14.220
For the next 10 years,

40:14.980 --> 40:16.230
Great Yan will not

40:17.260 --> 40:19.030
step into Biantang again.

40:26.200 --> 40:27.000
Your Majesty.

40:50.410 --> 40:51.280
Yan Xun...

40:52.820 --> 40:53.820
How I wish

40:54.870 --> 40:57.270
things could've ended differently for us.

41:20.360 --> 41:21.110
Your Highness,

41:21.110 --> 41:22.630
the time is ripe now.

41:22.660 --> 41:24.100
We must act immediately!

41:25.050 --> 41:27.020
The guilty official Sun Di
has stolen the military tally!

41:27.020 --> 41:28.020
It's utter treason!

41:28.020 --> 41:29.370
Seize him at once!

41:30.540 --> 41:31.170
Mother,

41:31.190 --> 41:32.520
you would surely

41:32.650 --> 41:33.770
be proud of me.

41:33.940 --> 41:34.580
We can

41:34.690 --> 41:36.170
finally put all of this behind us.

41:36.170 --> 41:37.700
Why couldn't you let him go?

41:37.810 --> 41:38.660
Li Ce

41:38.690 --> 41:40.890
was never worthy of the dragon robe
from the day he was born!
